      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776185494268,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "B_ref = 524,288 tokens (2¹⁹)\nBopt  = B_ref × (D / D_ref)^0.383\nη_scale = √(B / B_ref)\nλ_scale = √(B/B_ref) × (D_ref/D)\nτ_epoch = B/(n·D) = const  ← key invariant",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
