      "originalText": "B_ref = 524,288 tokens (2¹⁹)\nBopt  = B_ref × (D / D_ref)^0.383\nη_scale = √(B / B_ref)\nλ_scale = √(B/B_ref) × (D_ref/D)\nτ_epoch = B/(n·D) = const  ← key invariant",
